-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2010-02-28 Omm 0.1.0
Coldplug of network interfaces
Plugin loader

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2010-02-22 Omm 0.0.3

libomm has all the basic Upnp code, no dependency on libplatinum anymore
ommc, ommr and omms are ported to libomm with almost all functionality as with libplatinum
API is so much cleaner now
user interface for controller is a plugin so only the plugin is linked to the gui toolkit

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2009-04-15  OmmS

vdr-upnp 0.0.3
 cmake extracts API version from /usr/include/vdr and renames plugin .so file

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2009-04-15  OmmS

vdr-upnp 0.0.2
 changed number of children in top level containers (Live-TV, Recordings) from 0 to 1 to satisfy xbmc

 changed objectId of recordings from "/<channel id>/<start time>/" to 
 "vdr-rec/<channel id>/<start time>/" to satisfy xbmc

initial version of lsupnp 0.0.1

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2009-04-15  Omm 0.0.1
Initial version with basic features (list incomplete):

OmmC:
device discovery: select UPnP server/renderer, dynamicely add/remove server/renderer
browse: lazy browsing
transport: start, stop, pause, seek, position-info thread
render control: volume

OmmR:
engines: vlc, mplayer, xine
state machine
EOT detection
seek in streams
position-info thread

OmmS-vdr:
channel-list
recording-list
http server for recordings
handle 2GiB sliced VDR-recordings
seek in recordings

OmmSession:
epia image with Xorg and openchrome driver
